pfizer 's products include the blockbuster drug lipitor ( atorvastatin ) , used to lower ldl blood cholesterol ; lyrica ( pregabalin ) for neuropathic pain/fibromyalgia ; diflucan ( fluconazole ) , an oral antifungal medication ; zithromax ( azithromycin ) , an antibiotic ; viagra ( sildenafil ) for erectile dysfunction ; and celebrex/celebra ( celecoxib ) , an anti - inflammatory drug .

